					<h2>Order procedure</h2>
					<div class="contentHelpContLeft fl">
						<h3>Submit order: </h3>
						<p>
						When you select items, put them into shopping bag and click checkout to submit your orders. Don’t forget to sign in making it more easier! 
						Select the address where you wish to receive your package. Please double check the address you select when you have several addresses. </p>
						<br>						

						<h3>Service confirmation: </h3>
						<p>
						After you have submitted your order, our customer service will contact you to confirm the details (such as items, delivery rate, address and telephone number etc.) by Email/telephone. </p>
						<br>						

						<h3>Payment: </h3>
						<p>
						Pay for your order by our provided secured gateway . </p>
						<br>						

						<h3>Purchase: </h3>
						<p>
						Our purchase agents will purchase the items you order and update the delivery tracking number to your order list. Delivery tracking</p>
						<br>						

						<h3>Delivery: </h3>
						<p>
						Usually delivery will take 2~7 days depending on the delivery service you choose. After opening your package, you notice any problem (such as damaged goods) please contact us within 3 days, if we don’t hear anything from you within 3 days, we consider the transaction as successful. </p>

